<abstract><t>This document specifies combined use of H3 and LISP for mobility- networks: - Enabling real-time tile-by-tile localized-annotation of road-conditions - Sharing of road annotations: hazards, blockages, maintenance, furniture - Between MobilityClients, which produce-consume road-tile state information - Using formal in-network-state addressable- indexed-maintained by H3Servers.</t></abstract>

